{"tid":944811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"vtc無端端改我班","createTime":"2018-12-17T11:59:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T12:27:29.000Z","uid":226216,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"43eb1d6f7b249753cfb8368e3b7cba488a8db731","tid":944811,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"我剛讀梗HD，要揀科。<br />\n我揀左<span style=\"font-size: large;\">B</span>科，而A，C科（尤其<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></span>科）係我最唔想讀既科，我填選科表已經填左A係我<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">最唔想讀，最冇興趣</span></span>嘅科。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">拿，我係果d拿臨搞掂啲學費就唔使煩嘅人。</div>但因為我嗰幾日唔得閒所以冇去搞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">13號</span>佢出咗學費單，佢今日<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">17號</span>vtc先打嚟同我講：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「唔好意思，我哋搞錯咗呀，你所讀嘅科唔係B科，而係A科。」</span><br />\n<br />\n我吊你老母呀，好彩我冇早去交學費姐，如果唔係我咪俾錢去讀一個完全冇興趣嘅課程？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋點解你地可以咁冇交帶，話轉班就轉。一句話「搞錯咗」就算？<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">明明一開始就文件已經表示我係讀B科</span></span>，屌你老母突然間轉左去咁不負責任架咩？？？<br />\n<br />\n我係咪應該返去嘈佢，問可唔可以俾返B班個位我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以俾啲意見我？<br />\n關乎我人生㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f517a5a7b3947921d1ffa3db2e69549714f02600","tid":944811,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:02:45.000Z","msg":"是尻但啦"},{"pid":"7409d57bff34486d0cdcaf0c421c3ed3829d7ff6","tid":944811,"uid":166792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:04:35.000Z","msg":"慳返d 錢啦"},{"pid":"7ec70906cebe58bec2f2ec990206198922afaf53","tid":944811,"uid":210662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好讀咯<br />\n講咁多廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔係收左